Comment:
Yeah... sorry but no, thanks! Once you decide to ditch the original storyline you need to bring something really, really strong to the table, that surpasses it. If you take something away from people that they love, then bringing something similar is no longer enough. You aren't just met with high expectations anymore, you're also met with people missing their "loved ones". This makes them initially spiteful of the new content, you're handicapping yourself with this decision... and you need to deliver double the awesome to counter it. This? This just won't cut it.
I bet this season will fail hard, forcing you to either drop the series or continue the original. Thanks to how Max is, there would be quite a few cool ways of doing that; that story is far from over.
